subject: Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Draymond Green had 20 points and 10 rebounds, and No. 7 Michigan State beat No. 15 Wisconsin, 69-55, in East Lansing, Mich., to move back into a first-place tie with No. 6 Ohio State.
